<div id="detailsModalGuarantee" class="details-modal">

  <!-- Modal content -->
  <div class="details-modal-content pr" style="max-width: 480px;">
        <span class="spanGuarantee color--blue">&times;</span>
    <div class="inner">
        <h1 class="sans--large color--blue fw--600 lowercase pb2" temprop="name">if you don’t love it, we’ll take it back.</h1>
        <p class="sans--body color--blue fw--400 pb2">we stand behind our satisfaction guarantee. if you’re unhappy with the results, we’ll refund your first order, minus shipping and handling. to request a refund, please send an email to hello@beamtlc.com with your name, order confirmation number, and reason for the request, within 30 days of receiving your shipment.</p>
